column2: "The body you see in this bio-fluid..."
"There was an error when trying to upload your data into the 4th clone."
"There was a data mismatch with the specimen known as 909."
"Subject 909 is right here, and yet you're standing right there."
"Remember how I mentioned the ARKS we found in cold sleep?"

"While we were proceeding with our research into the New ARKS,
we were also managing strict control over the equipment that houses them."

"During one of the armed conflicts, one of our storage facilities
was attacked, and said equipment went missing."
"Could it be possible that you're the..."
"I have no idea what you're talking about."
"My first memory is of being sent down to Halpha."
"You don't seem to be telling a lie."
"It seems the Starless have noticed our presence."
